    title: 'Signs Your Commercial Roof Needs Coating (Not Replacement)',
    slug: 'signs-commercial-roof-needs-coating',
    excerpt:
      'Roof replacement isn\'t always the answer. Learn the telltale signs that your commercial roof is a strong candidate for a coating system that costs 50-70% less than full replacement.',
    date: '2026-04-10',
    category: 'Roof Coating',
