    slug: 'tpo-vs-epdm-vs-pvc-commercial-roofing',
    excerpt:
      'A head-to-head comparison of the three most common commercial roofing membranes, with cost data, performance characteristics, and recommendations for Charlotte building owners.',
    date: '2026-04-13',
    category: 'Roof Coating',
