    slug: 'commercial-roof-maintenance-schedule',
    excerpt:
      'A proactive maintenance schedule is the single most effective way to extend your commercial roof\'s lifespan and avoid costly emergency repairs. Here\'s the complete maintenance calendar for Charlotte building owners.',
